    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this car to believe it. It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, it looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor today! Not a single scratch or smudge\u2014it\u2019s truly in pristine, flawless condition. I\u2019ve babied this ride since day one, and it drives like an absolute dream. If you\u2019re looking for perfection without the brand-new price tag, this is the one for you. Come take a look, you definitely won't be disappointed!",
