    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This 996.2 Carrera 4S represents a pinnacle of analog feedback and mechanical refinement. The M96 3.6L flat-six features a documented LN Engineering IMS bearing retrofit and a recently replaced rear main seal. Power is managed via a G96.01 6-speed transaxle and a viscous-coupling AWD system derived from the Turbo. The chassis benefits from a wide-body stance and factory M030 suspension, providing exceptional lateral grip. Braking performance is superlative, utilizing 'Big Red' four-piston monobloc calipers over cross-drilled rotors. Meticulously preserved with a verified DME overrev report showing no Range 2 ignitions, this C4S is a turn-key collector-grade specimen.",
      "price": 48900.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 48
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Single owner. Garage kept. No accidents. Full service history. Flawless paint and interior. Mechanical inspection welcome.",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 48
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This is a rare opportunity to own a truly showroom-quality vehicle that has been meticulously preserved since day one. Finished in a deep, lustrous metallic paint that has been protected by a multi-stage ceramic coating, the exterior is absolutely flawless\u2014no rock chips, swirl marks, or door dings to be found. The wheels are pristine with zero curb rash, wrapped in high-performance tires with ample tread. Inside, the cabin still retains that new-car aroma; the premium leather seats show no signs of bolster wear or creasing, and every piece of switchgear operates with a satisfying, tactile precision. This car has been strictly garage-kept in a climate-controlled environment and has never seen rain. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, featuring a full, documented service history from the local dealership. Every fluid flush and inspection was performed ahead of schedule. Included with the sale are both original keys, the owner's manual portfolio, and the original window sticker. For the discerning buyer who demands perfection, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of its class.",
      "price": 44800.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
