    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "This FD3S RX-7 is a superlative example of rotary performance, featuring a factory-spec 13B-REW engine with verified compression integrity across all rotor faces. The sequential twin-turbocharger setup provides a seamless transition and immediate spooling, maintaining a flat torque curve through the high-revving powerband. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise five-speed manual transmission and a Torsen limited-slip differential, ensuring tactile feedback and optimal corner-exit traction. The chassis retains its original torsional rigidity, complemented by an unmolested double-wishbone suspension and four-piston braking calipers. Every vacuum line and thermal component has been vetted for longevity, making this a mechanically transparent, turn-key investment for the serious enthusiast.",
